Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.87,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}toikakete kurukawaita kaze ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.87,0:22:31.41,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}fuwari mau hana hitohira
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:43.76,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}itsuka itsuka to himeru awaku senmei na kage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:50.31,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}mada koko de iki wo surukarenu itami to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.31,0:22:59.57,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}anata wo matsu sore dake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:18.21,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}nanige nai shiawase ikiru kono sekai de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:13.90,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Tudo se foi tão naturalmente,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:20.23,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}buscando uma simples felicidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.87,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}No vento seco que me desafia,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.87,0:22:31.41,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}uma única flor voando.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:43.76,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Um dia, em algum lugar, a sombra tênue e radiante se esconderá.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:50.31,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Ainda estou aqui e respirando, aguentando essa dor,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.31,0:22:59.57,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}apenas esperando por você.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:18.21,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Encontrando uma simples felicidade neste mundo em que vivo.
